            <div class="crs-pillar coral crs-reveal delay-2"><p class="crs-pillar-num">03</p><p class="crs-pillar-title">Excellence Opérationnelle</p><p class="crs-pillar-desc">Outils, Méthodes, Technologie</p></div>
